claim.claim-text:
A program causing a computer to function as:
a first display control unit configured to perform display control of a cell image with one or a plurality of images including cells;
a second display control unit configured to perform display control such that a part or all of a motion amount generated for each of subregions with the one or the plurality of images is associated with each of the subregions, and are superimposed on the cell image and displayed.
